00:35:00,307 --> 00:35:02,560
DA Chase says that he is
gonna plead guilty to everything.

602
00:35:02,726 --> 00:35:05,570
Councilwoman Pollard,
this is Rene Ramirez.

603
00:35:05,729 --> 00:35:07,606
He works very closely
with Deputy Mayor Lance,

604
00:35:07,856 --> 00:35:12,453
and he is a very, very vocal proponent
of gun ownership rights.

605
00:35:13,445 --> 00:35:16,289
Freedom isn't free.
Not even the freedom to bear arms.

606
00:35:16,698 --> 00:35:20,498
So, Mr. Ramirez and I got together
and came up with this.

