00:35:21,953 --> 00:35:23,705
Citywide gun control ordinances.

609
00:35:24,039 --> 00:35:27,543
Nothing that makes it harder
to buy or own or carry a gun.

610
00:35:27,709 --> 00:35:32,385
It also doesn't prohibit people from
protecting themselves from gun violence.

611
00:35:35,050 --> 00:35:37,724
Okay, I'm gonna back you on this.
If for no other reason

