Ma'am, please. Hello? Hello?

632
00:36:41,616 --> 00:36:43,289
Son of a bitch!

633
00:36:44,244 --> 00:36:47,623
<i>Damien Darhk, the man
behind tonight's siege of Star City,</i>

634
00:36:47,789 --> 00:36:51,134
